            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Talking about the Latinx community and how that are of Gatlinburg wasn't rebuilt, how would you describe the reconstruction efforts in general?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 17</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
