            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">2021_02_03_Rivera_Christian_Q24</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>As a young person who lived through this event, how would you say this event affected your life, the trajectory of it, or emotionally?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
